{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_01",
  "title": "バーチャル・\nシンガー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……いよいよね\nみんな、準備はいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… It's finally here.\nIs everyone ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.6280723573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8347389381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！\n……もしかして瑠依ちゃん、緊張してる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\n… Rui-chan‚ are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8347389381,
      "endTime": 12.6895461242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.8962126573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "少しだけね……今回は、特別なライブだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just a little… Because this time‚ it's a special live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8962126573,
      "endTime": 17.9383896669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.1383897146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんにしてはめずらしいなぁ\nむしろうちは楽しみ過ぎて震えとるわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's unusual for Rui-chan‚ isn't it?\nWell‚ I'm shaking with excitement~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1383897146,
      "endTime": 24.742721017199997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.949387455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね！　なんてったって今日は……\nミクちゃんとの共演ライブだもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! After all…\nIt's a joint live with Miku-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.949387455,
      "endTime": 31.206779670699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん！　私も今、凄くワクワクしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! I'm really excited right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4,
      "endTime": 36.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルとの共演、ずっと心待ちにしていたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been looking forward to this joint live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0666666667,
      "endTime": 40.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……分身の術が使えたらなぁ\nもう一人のうちは客席から観られたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… If only I could use the Clone Jutsu.\nThe other me could have watched from the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3666666667,
      "endTime": 48.426311692199995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの、まったく\nでも……みんなと話して、少し緊張もほぐれたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about‚ really.\nBut… after talking with everyone‚ I feel a little less nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6333333333,
      "endTime": 55.3471352896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ありのままに、想いのままに……\n今日のライブを、四人で楽しもう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being true to ourselves‚ expressing our feelings…\nLet's enjoy today's live together‚ the four of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5666666667,
      "endTime": 61.514591884400005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　……あ、でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! …Oh‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7,
      "endTime": 68.6195466042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今のうちに、みんなへ伝えておきたいことがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before we start‚ there's something I want to tell everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8666666667,
      "endTime": 69.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4666666667,
      "endTime": 70.87800450729999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数ヶ月前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few months ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666666667,
      "endTime": 73.3066667001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ出演のオファー、ですか？\n私達、TRINITYAiLEに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it an offer to perform at a live?\nFor us‚ TRINITYAiLE?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5333333333,
      "endTime": 79.74606111589999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。あるアーティストのイベントだ\n初音ミクって聞いたことあるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It's for an artist's event.\nHave you heard of Hatsune Miku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "endTime": 85.88115604960001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "は……\nは、初音ミクー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…\nH-Hatsune Miku!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0666666667,
      "endTime": 90.0257823944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "うわ、びっくりした\n優ちゃんがそんな声上げるの、めずらしいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ that surprised me.\nIt's rare to hear Yu-chan raising her voice like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2,
      "endTime": 97.3614056548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "だだ、だって初音ミクって……！\nえ、なんでテンション高いのうちだけなん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ because Hatsune Miku is…!\nEh‚ why am I the only one getting excited!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5666666667,
      "endTime": 103.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、あまり詳しくなくて\n名前は聞いたことがあるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I don't know much about her.\nI've heard the name before‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5333333333,
      "endTime": 108.8251457953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。私も、同級生に聴いてるって人がいて\n曲を聴かせてもらったことがあるくらいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. I know someone in my class who listens to her.\nI've been shown some of her songs before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0333333333,
      "endTime": 118.4236728708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "そっかぁ……\n……{user}さんはもちろん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\n…What about you‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6333333333,
      "endTime": 122.8871078491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ\n広い世代に人気のバーチャル・シンガー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ yeah.\nShe's a virtual singer popular across a wide range of generations…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "endTime": 127.86666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そうです！\n十数年前の8月31日、突如ネットの世界に現れた歌姫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right!\nShe appeared in the online world on August 31 over a decade ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0666666667,
      "endTime": 135.6630385082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "既存の概念や方法論に囚われない自由な音楽性と\n聴き手の心へダイレクトに響く歌声……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She has a free musical style that isn't bound by existing concepts or methodologies.\nHer singing voice resonates directly with the listener's heart…",
